Product Name: Thule Awning Omnistor 6300 12v Motor Kit
Product Description:
Thule Omnistor 6300 12v Motor Kit

The perfect upgrade for the Omnistor 6300

This Omnistor 6300 12V motor kit makes it easy to set up your home away from home. This motorised kit is capable of automatically deploying a Thule Omnistor 6300 awning, saving you the trouble of deploying the awning fabric. 

Versatile control

Even with this motor installed, you still have the option to manually override the motor and pitch your awning by hand. An optional relay can also be connected to your vehicle, which prevents the awning motor from deploying the awning when your vehicle is moving. The awning also comes in multiple colours to match your existing Omnistor awning, and only weighs an extra 1kg.

Thule Omnistor 6300 12v Motor Kit Features:

  • Can be retrofitted to Thule Omnistor 6300 awnings
  • Only 3cm additional length to awning cassette
  • Weighs 1kg
  • Optional relay to prevent deployment when vehicle is in motion
  • Multiple colour options available
  • Product no. 308096, 308097, 308098

Fiamma F45s Awning Bracket Ducato Boxer Relay H2 L2/ L3/ L4 Campervan with Roof Bars
Product Description:
Fiamma F45s Awning Adapter Kit for Ducato Boxer Relay H2 Campervans with Roof Bars

The Fiamma F45s Awning Adapter Kit is designed for the 2006 onwards Fiat Ducato, Citroen Jumper and Peugeot Boxer campervan with an already existing roof rack, suitable for a campervan H2 roof and a short, medium, long and extra-long wheel base (L1/ L2/L3/L4) camper van.

Should I go for the Fiamma F80s or the F45s awning?

In most situations the Fiamma F80s awning and F80s adapter kit is the preferred option against the F45 since this uses the already existing fixing points on the camper van meaning there's no need to drill into the body.  Please note the Fiamma F8Os awning is not compatible with campervans that already have a roof rack as they use the same fixing points, it's either one or the other.

The Fiamma F45s can be used along side a roof rack

The Fiamma F45s Awning Adapter Kit however allows for the Fiamma F45s awning to sit on the edge of the roof, this clears the existing fixing points which means it can be used along side a roof rack.

Sizes

  • Ducato, Jumper, Boxer L2 (Vehicle Length 5416mm): Fiamma F45s 300cm
  • Ducato, Jumper, Boxer L3 (Vehicle Length 5998mm): Fiamma F45s 375cm
  • Ducato, Jumper, Boxer L4 (Vehicle Length 6363mm): Fiamma F45s 400cm

Product Name: Easy Camp Voss Campervan Sun Canopy Awning
Product Description:
Easy Camp Voss Canopy

Motor Tour Sun Shade Awning for Campervan 

The perfect companion for spontaneous adventure, the Easy Camp Voss Canopy minimises set-up time, helping you to make the most of your day at the beach, campsite, outdoor event, or wherever you need a versatile extra layer of shelter from the sun or rain! The Voss Canopy is quickly and easily pitched, using two sturdy steel poles which fit neatly into brass eyelets, and are secured by twin guy lines. The clever design of the Easy Camp sun canopy awning also features side flaps which provide both additional shelter, and a second anchor point for the guy lines, considerably improving stability.

Varied attachment canopy height

For added flexibility, the Easy Camp Voss Canopy has an attachment height between 150-260cm so is suitable for a range of campervans and motorhomes and connected by a 5 and 7mm kador beading. The flysheet consists of a Polyurethane (PU) coated 100% polyester fabric, making it a lightweight yet highly waterproof canopy for sitting under during rain showers. 19mm steel poles and high visibility guy lines provide a rigid and reliable pitch.

Product Name: Truma Combi 2E 4E 6E D4E, D6E Boiler and Space Heater Kit 2 with Ducting
Product Description:
Truma Combi 2E 4E 6E D4E D6E Water Boiler and Space Heater

Truma kit 2 for campervan and motorhome

The Truma Combi is a popular choice for heating both water and living space in your campervan, motorhome or caravan. The Combi 2E, 4E and 6E are energy efficient, quiet in operation and incredibly compact and lightweight for the performance it offers. The Truma kit 2 includes all the items needed for installation including a digital wall-mounted control panel which is iNet ready*. With the addition of a Truma iNet system you can conveniently control the Combi from your mobile phone using Bluetooth via an app. Additionally, if you have a Truma air-conditioning unit installed, the control panel can automatically co-ordinate the heater and air conditioning unit to ensure your living space maintains a comfortable and controlled environment.

The Truma 2E, 4E and 6E feature an integrated 10 litre stainless steel water tank. Suitable for all seasons, it allows for independent heating of hot water in summer mode as well as both hot water and warm air in winter mode. Able to operate on either 230V electric mains voltage or on LPG, the Combi provides hot water, and a warm campervan, motorhome, or caravan, whether on a camping site, or in the wild. You can even use both electric and gas energy sources in unison for rapid heating times.

The newly available D4E and D6E models feature the same compact design and integrated 10L water tank. Included in these models is the Truma iNet X Panel for advanced digital control and system monitoring your campervan or motorhome.

Please note, to use the Truma iNet system with your Combi, you will need a Truma iNet controller (Not included in 2E, 4E, or 6E kits), available to purchase HERE.

The Truma Combi kit 2 contains:

  • Truma Combi LPG gas and 230V electric unit
  • Truma CP Plus digital wall mounted control panel
  • John Guest connection kit
  • 10m of 65mm heater ducting pipe
  • Truma cowl cover
  • 8 x Truma heating clips
  • 4 x Truma blown air heating nut
  • 4 x black Truma end outlets with throttle

Please note that the Truma Room Temperature Sensor Cable is not included in the kit.

Product Name: Thetford Linear Bowl and Hob Campervan & Motorhome Sink & Cooker Combo
Product Description:
Thetford Linear Bowl & Hob Campervan & Motorhome Sink & Cooker Combo

The simple, rectangular kitchen sink for leisure vehicles

This simple, deep sink is great for larger vehicles. With this sink you won't feel compromised in space in your kitchen. A large 12.1 litre capacity provides ample space for washing up, and the sturdy stainless steel construction ensures it's up to the job. A glass lid keeps your sink safe during transit, and lets you use it as an extra worktop when it's not in use. The linear bowl is great for larger campervans, van conversions, motorhomes and caravans.

This campervan bowl sink comes complete with a 19mm water drain and an invisible foam seal, making it easy to fit in your campervan, motorhome or caravan.

A large, rectangular cooker for that at-home kitchen feel

Thetford's Linear Hob gives you four hobs set in a square, just like a traditional home stove-top cooker. This high-quality cooker lets you take tasty cooking with you wherever you go. The efficient use of space gives it a compact, fully featured design, with a glass lid to allow it to double up as extra worktop space when not in use.

You can start cooking with the press of a button thanks to the 12v ignition, and detachable pan supports make this stovetop easy to clean and maintain. Four durable stainless steel burners, each individually controllable by the sleek matte nickel teardrop dials, make this a capable campervan cooker.

Thetford Linear Bowl Features:

  • Stainless steel construction
  • Handy glass lid
  • Fixed with invisible foam seal
  • 12.1L capacity
  • Lightweight 3.4kg design
  • 19mm water drain included
  • No tap hole
  • Measures 135 x 360 x 550mm (h x w x d)
  • Worktop cut-out dimensions - 315 x 505 mm (w x d)

Thetford Linear Hob Features:

  • Stainless steel hob burners
  • Handy glass lid
  • Elegant matte nickel teardrop control knobs
  • Powerful four hob design
  • Detachable pan supports
  • Surface mounted fixation
  • Lightweight 7.0Kg design
  • 12v ignition included
  • Gas burners: 1 x 1.0 kW, 2x 1.5 kW & 1x 2.5 kW
  • Total heat output: 6.5kW
  • Measures 110 x 520 x 550 mm (h x w x d)
  • Worktop cut-out dimensions - 491 x 518 mm (w x d)
Product Warranty: Thetford products come with a three-year warranty. In the case of malfunction within the warranty period, Thetford will replace or repair the product.

Product Name: Fiamma F45 Zip Motorhome and Caravan Privacy Room
Product Description:
Fiamma F45 Zip Motorhome and Caravan Privacy Room

This Product is the Privacy Room only. Which can only be installed on the Fiamma Zip wind-out awning found here:

The Fiamma F45 Zip Privacy Room is a great way to add extra living space to your motorhome or caravan. It is made of high-quality materials and is designed to withstand all weather conditions.

Quick and Easy to fit

The privacy room is easy to install and can be attached to your awning in just a few minutes. The two side panels simply zip straight to the awning canopy, Half of a YKK® zip is already stitched to the outer side edges of the canopy. The front panel slides into the front bar of the awning. Then just zip the corners together and you're almost done! Peg down and you're ready.

Whats in the Box?

  • Front Panel with 1 opening window and mosquito net,*
  • 2 Side Panels with 1 opening window in each and mosquito net,
  • Rapid Set aluminium tension poles,
  • Vehicle skirting,
  • Curtains for all three windows,
  • Mega Bag,
  • Optional as an Extra**, Side Panel with a Zipped in Door,
  • Suits mounting to the vehicle at heights of between 225 centimetres and 280 centimetres from the ground,


* please note, there are photographs on the wider web, not our site, showing two windows in the front panels, these are not actually available and are of an awning set up and photographed with two small front panels!   

The Fiamma Zip awning and privacy room are available to purchase separately. This means that you can buy the awning first and add the privacy room later if desired. However, it is important to note that standard privacy rooms are not compatible with Zip awnings, and vice versa.

Outwell ECOcool 24L Cool Box 12V/230V - Slate Grey
Product Description:
Outwell ECOcool 24L Cool Box 12V/230V - Slate Grey

Eco Electric Coolbox

Outwell's ECOcool Cool Box provides high-quality cooling performance. Thanks to its thermally efficient, insulated design, this cool box provides strong performance without draining your car or motorhome leisure battery. The cooler's efficiency ensures your food and drinks are kept cool while still leaving you with the power to run your other appliances. 

Great as a home cool box, great as a camping cool box

The versatile design of this cool box lets it excel in multiple environments. Well suited to camping trips, picnics and festivals, it can run off the 12V provided by your battery. At home however you can use the 230V provided by you mains outlets, making this great for parties. You can also select two cooling settings - ECOcool, or Max cooling. 

Cool box or heater

The Outwell ECOcool isn't limited to cooling, either. Whilst as a cooler it can reduce take your food and drinks 18-25 °C below the outside temperature, it can raise the temperature by 50-60 °C, allowing you to keep food warm for guests. These versatile features, combined with the robust finish and fold-flat handle, make it a great choice for a range of events.

Outwell ECOcool Cool Box features:

  • Can operate on both 12V and 230V
  • Two cooling settings
  • Cools to 18-25 °C  below ambient
  • In warming mode, can warm by 50-60 °C
  • Includes internal ice-pack divider
  • Storage compartment uses antimicrobial materials
  • Fold-flat carry handle
Product Warranty: Outwell cooler boxes come with a two-year warranty.
Product Availability: The Outwell ECOcool cool box is sent via next working day delivery

  • Hook track system

  • Carry bag

Outwell Newburg 160 fits:

  • Ford Transit 

Size:

  • Pack size: 78 x 36 x 27 cm
  • Weight: 13.6 kg

Product Name: Easy Camp Fairfields Drive Away Awning Tent for Campervans
Product Description:
Easy Camp Fairfields Drive-Away Awning for Campervans 

The quick and easy way to expand your campervans space

This Easy Camp Fairfields Drive-Away awning is a great addition to T4, T5 and T6 campervans, as well as other similar sized campers and MPVs with a mounting height of between 180 and 205cm. This drive-away awning connects to your vehicle while it's parked up at your pitch and is freestanding when you're out for the day, allowing you to explore in your campervan without having to pack up your awning each time you leave. 

Secure, lightweight fitting & installation

Pre-angled fibreglass poles provide stability & rigidity, enabling the awning to free stand securely. Decoupling the awning from your campervan or motorhome is a quick and easy process, allowing you to leave quickly. Weatherproof ventilation opposite the main door helps to prevent condensation, and a detachable groundsheet gives you a luxury feeling. A toggle-up large window gives you sunlight when you want it, too.

Easy Camp Fairfields Driveaway awning kit features:

Product Description:
Outwell Newburg 240 Air Tall Drive-Away Awning for Campervans

Tall drive away awning suitable for motorhomes and van conversions

This tall variant of the Outwell Newburg is designed to provide compatibility with taller campervans, motorhomes and van conversions. The awning attaches to vehicles with a rail height of 240-270cm via either 5mm or 7mm beadings, providing you with an easy and quick pitching.

Premium design

Apart from the higher awning bead, the Newburg 240 Air Tall shares the same features as the standard Newburg 240 Air for smaller campervans. It uses Outwell's Outtex 4000 Select 100% polyester fabric, which has a hydrostatic head of 4000mm, ensuring you and your family inside stay dry. It also uses rigid, pre-shaped air tubes instead of poles, simplifying pitching. Guy ropes increase stability also, helping your awning resist the wind.

Can sleep two

The optional Newburg 240 Inner Tent allows this awning to sleep two, whilst still providing extra space and without blocking access to the main doors or your vehicle. This makes it a great choice for growing families.

  • Large tinted windows reducing glare and ensuring privacy
  • HookTrack System for versatile positioning of lights and items up to 1.5kg

Product Name: Dometic RM 10.5T 3-Way Fridge Freezer Caravan & Motorhome
Product Description:
Dometic RM 10.5T 3-Way Absorption Fridge

Smart Absorption Under-counter Fridge Freezer for Caravan and Motorhomes

The new Dometic RM10 series fridges bring with them a new level of performance. Designed for use in caravan and motorhomes, the RM 10.5T 12v 230v refrigerator comes equipped with a TFT colour display panel, as well as a simple turn/push button, giving you easy control over your fridge's cooling output. 

Flexible fridge cooling

The Dometic RM10.5T 3-way fridge freezer can be powered by either gas, 12V battery power or 230V mains power. What's more, the fridge is able to automatically switch between each power source, giving you one less thing to worry about on your holiday. The double-hinged door can open from either side, too, making it easy to access wherever you install it. This Dometic 3 way under counter fridge also features a removable freezer compartment, allowing you to maximise on your fridge's volume if you desire.

Elegant design

The sleek design of the RM 10.5T camper fridge is beautifully finished with aluminium handles. Full side interior LED lighting makes it easy to use your fridge, and a noiseless design on all 3 power types ensures a good nights sleep. It's not all design, though. Dometic have integrated their latest Smart CI-BUS technology into this fridge, which enables it to communicate with the latest control panels in caravans and motor homes. 

Dometic RM10.5T 3-Way Fridge features:

  • Double-hinged door
  • Colour TFT control panel
  • 3-way power: gas, 230v & 12V compatible
  • Easy front control dial
  • Removable freezer compartment
  • Two slim veg crisper trays
  • Full side LED interior light
  • Noiseless absorption cooling on 12v, 230v and LPG

The Dometic RM 10.5T replaces the following fridges:

  • Dometic: RM 400R, RM 400 P/C, RM 415, RM 4400, RM 4401LM, RM 4405LM, RM 6401, RM 7401 L, RM 7405 L, RM 850x
  • Thetford: N100 1P, N100 2E, N100 6E, N100 6A, N3100A, N3104A, N3100E, N3104E, N4100E+, N4100A, N4104E+, N4104A, N1041P, N1042E, N1046E, N1046A

Please note - the measurements of the RM 10.5T may not be exactly the same as your previous fridge model - check measurements carefully! The RM 10.5T is delivered on a pallet.

SPECIAL/SECOND AVAILABLE

(JC-SP-3366) Dometic RM 10.5S -- Issue: Deep score on RHS and insulation tube at the back is dented. Tatty box. -- £925

For more information and photos, Please contact our Customer Service team on 0151 334 0222

Product Name: Dometic RMS 10.5T 3-Way Wheel Arch Fridge for Campervan & Motorhome
Product Description:
Dometic RMS 10.5T Wheel Arch Fridge for Campervan and Motorhomes

All the features of the Dometic RM10.5T, but with a compact design

The Dometic RMS 10.5T 3 way fridge packs all the same features as the full-size RM10.5T, but with a reduced lower volume to accommodate the wheel-arch of your vehicle. This allows you to maximise the space in your vehicle. In doing so, it retains much of the volume of the larger camper fridge, only dropping 10L to provide a total storage volume of 83L. 

Flexible performance

A double door hinge allows the door to open on both the left and right, making it suitable for a range of installation points in campervans, motorhomes, caravans and boats. What's more, the Dometic 10.5T is a 3-way fridge, meaning it can be powered by gas, 12V and 230V. The fridge is able to automatically switch between these power sources, allowing you to holiday with peace of mind. This camping fridge also has a removable freezer compartment, allowing you to find a storage configuration that works for your trip.

The modern cooling solution

The Dometic RMS10.5T fridge comes equipped with a TFT colour display, which lets you monitor your fridge's cooling & clearly see what power source is being used. The sleek design, with aluminium handles and simple push/turn knob give you excellent control over the fridge, while internal LED lighting make it easy to find what you're looking for inside. Dometic have also equipped this fridge with their Smart CI-BUS system, which enables your 3-way fridge to communicate seamlessly with the latest campervan and caravan control panels. Thanks to its absorption refrigeration technology, this fridge can operate in near total silence. This makes it perfect for campervans, as it ensures you can get a good nights sleep.

Dometic RMS10.5T 3-Way Fridge Features:

  • Dual-hinge doors can open from both sides
  • 3-pay power on gas, 12V or 230V
  • Automatic power switching
  • Colour TFT screen to monitor power source usage & cooling performance
  • Turn/push knob dial to control fridge
  • Reduced lower profile to accommodate vehicle wheel arch
  • Removable freezer compartment
  • Internal LED lighting
  • Ultra quiet operation 

This Dometic RMS 10.5T absorption fridge replaces the following Dometic & Thetford fridge models:

  • Dometic: Rm 300 P/A / RM 301 / RM 4290L / RM 4300 / RM 6291 / Rm 7290L / RM 7291L / RMS 850x
  • Thetford: N3090A / N3090E / N4090A / N4100A / N4100E+ / N901P / N902E / N3097A / N3097E / N4097A / N4097E

Please note - the RMS 10.5T may not have exactly the same measurements as your old fridge - check measurements carefully!

Product Name: Dometic RMS 10.5XP Extra-Deep Absorption Fridge
Product Description:
Dometic RMS 10.5XP Extra Deep Cabinet Fridge

High-capacity absorption fridge for campervan and motorhome

The Dometic RMS 10.5XP absorption fridge replaces the RMS 10.5XP refrigerator. Providing a deep profile for increased storage volume, making it perfect for touring use. The RMS 10.5XP fridge comes with 98 litres of volume and internal LED lighting.

Double hinged absorption fridge freezer

Featuring innovative door hinges, which allow your fridge door to open on both the left or the right, for flexible installation. With a removable freezer compartment and twin crisper trays to organise your food easily, ensuring long lasting freshness. And as an RMS model, this fridge has a reduced lower profile, allowing it to fit snugly over the wheel arch of your campervan, motorhome or caravan. The perfect retrofit kitchen upgrade when you only have limited space.

Sleek design, 3-way power & easy control

The Dometic RMS10.5XP is a 3-way fridge - this means it can be powered on gas (propane or butane), 12v (typical car or leisure battery voltage) or 230v (mains hookup). What's more, it can automatically switch between these power sources, letting you focus on enjoying your holiday. Despite the technology behind this fridge, its isn't complicated to use. A simple TFT colour display panel lets you monitor the power source in use, and the twist/push control knob makes it easy to tune your fridge's cooling performance. Dometic have also included their latest Smart CI-BUS technology with this fridge, which lets it communicate seamlessly with the latest campervan and caravan control panels.

Dometic Absorption Fridge Key Features:

  • Dual-hinge doors which can open on both sides
  • Aluminium door handles
  • 3-way power (12v, 230v & gas (propane or butane))
  • Automatic power switching
  • Colour TFT display panel to monitor power type in use
  • Utilises ultra-quiet absorption refrigeration technology
  • Removable freezer compartment
  • Internal LED lighting

Product Description:
Dometic RML 10.4P 3-Way Absorption 3 Way Fridge Freezer

New Generation Slim Tower Fridge with TFT Display

Big on space, big on performance

The Dometic RML 10.4P fridge freezer provides enough space for you to go touring with your family without feeling compromised in the kitchen. The Dometic RML 10.4P replaces the Dometic RML 10.4T absorption fridge. With 133L of space, the RML10.4P fridge ensure you can carry as much as you need in your campervan, caravan, motorhome or boat. This fridge features Dometic's patented double-hinged door which can be hung left and right. The freezer compartment can also be opened left or right and is easily removed if you need more space for refrigerated items.

Cool innovation

This Dometic 3-way fridge can operate on 12V, 230V and butane or propane gas, giving you great flexibility. A removable freezer lets you store your food in a way that works for you, and integrated LED light strips give you an excellent view of the interior. The included VG fresh fruit and veg crisper drawers let you perfectly preserve your fruit and veg with humidity control.

Easy control

The Dometic RML10.4P comes equipped with a TFT colour screen, which lets you monitor the power source currently in use. The fridge is able to automatically switch between power sources, making it easy to manage your energy usage.

Dometic RML10.4P 3-Way Fridge Features:

  • Innovative dual-hinge door can be opened from both sides
  • 3-way power for gas, 12v and 240v use
  • Elegant aluminium door handles extend over complete fridge height
  • Colour TFT panel to monitor performance
  • Tall tower design with 133L total internal volume
  • Integrated LED lighting strips
  • Removable freezer compartment

Dometic RMD 10.5P 153 Litre Campervan & Caravan Fridge Freezer

Upgrade to new levels of cool

The Dometic RMD 10.5P compressor fridge provides unprecedented levels of convenience & control. The doors open from both the left & the right thanks to clever double hinges, a TFT display lets you monitor the cooling performance, and the fridge can automatically switch between 3 different power sources. Fridge, Freezer, Fashion

An LED light bar makes it easy to use at any time of day, and a dual-point door locking system gives you extra security. The freezer compartment is removable, too, allowing you to maximise on freezer space when you need it. Dometic's innovative VG-fresh crisper trays include adjustable humidity, allowing you to preserve your fruit and veg perfectly.

Next generation performance

The RMD 10.5P camper fridge is powered by absorption refrigeration technology, which gives it ultra-quiet cooling on all three power sources. This makes it perfect for when your family needs a good nights sleep after a long day of travelling. Dometic have also equipped this camper fridge with Dometic's new Smart CI-BUS system, allowing it to communicate seamlessly with the latest caravan and campervan control panels. 

Dometic RMD 10.5P 12v Fridge Freezer Features:

  • Dual-hinge doors open from each side
  • Colour TFT screen to monitor cooling performance
  • Ultra-quiet operation
  • Can operate on gas, 12V or 230V

Dometic RCS 10.5T Wheel Arch Fridge 12V
Product Description:
Dometic RCS 10.5T Wheel Arch Fridge 12V

Powerful and versatile campervan refrigerator

The RCS 10.5T is equipped with 83 litres of internal volume, making it great for campervan, motorhome, caravan or boat touring. This wheel-arch model is designed with a cut-out at the rear, making it perfect for fitting over the wheel arch of your camper or caravan, allowing you to maximise on your vehicle's space. This state-of-the-art Dometic 10 series refrigerator is the perfect upgrade an older refrigeration unit. The freezer compartment is removable, too, letting you configure your fridge to your specific needs.

Smart refrigeration

The RCS10.5T camper fridge is powered by 12v, and as a compressor fridge it does so with great efficiency. It also includes an integrated colour TFT screen to monitor your cooling performance, as well as a simple twist/push control dial. Dometic have also equipped this fridge with Dometic Smart CI-BUS technology, allowing it to communicate seamlessly with many smart controllers.

Elegant styling

The slick black finish of this fridge adds a sophisticated edge to any motorhome, campervan or caravan. Each door includes innovative double hinges, allowing them to open on both sides. They also use a double-locking system, and the insides are softly lit by LED light strips. Aluminium handles make it easy to open the fridge on both the left and right. The interior of this compressor fridge includes two slim crisper drawers, perfect for storing your fruit and veg apart to preserve them to perfection.

Silent operation

The RCS 10.5T 12v compressor fridge comes equipped with a silent mode, which can be easily activated by use of the TFT screen, allowing you to sleep with peace. A boost function allows this camper fridge to provide on-demand cooling when you need it, putting you in control of your fridge - or you can simply leave the camper fridge to it, and let its automatic management systems optimise its performance.

The modern, powerful compressor refrigerator

The Dometic RCS 10.5XT 12v fridge gives you ample storage and cooling power in a compact package. Large, powerful performance

The Dometic RCL 10.4ET camper fridge offers plenty of space. With a mighty 157 litres of internal volume, it's a great pick for touring use or extended trips. Camp in luxury with a premium Dometic 12v compressor fridge

This refrigerator also uses Dometic Smart CI-Bus technology, allowing it to communicate with many smart controllers effortlessly. Wish your van had more space? Kampa's Cross AIR awning makes it easy to expand the space available to your and your family while camping, without a lengthy setup. Reliable comfort

Drive away awnings let you reserve your pitch, ensuring you can return to your favourite spot after travelling in your campervan or motorhome. This awning also comes with multiple inflation points, ensuring your awning isn't reliant on a single air beam.

  • Removeable zip panels

This tunnel awning uses inflatable air technology, making it quick and easy to pitch. It uses four inflation points, making any air leaks easy to isolate and repair. 

Double inner bedroom tent

Wish you had a bigger van, so you could bring more friends or family camping? With this awning, you can continue to rely on your trusty campervan. Two inner sleeping tents have room for four guests to sleep, ensuring you don't feel limited by your vehicle. These sleeping tents use a darkened fabric, ensuring a good night's sleep. Even with these tents occupied however, the awning's generous dimensions provide a large living area.

Flexible family touring

Kampa have produced both a left-hand and right-hand version of this awning, allowing you to choose the awning which bets suits your vehicle. They also offer two different fabrics - the standard Touring AIR uses their weatherproof 68D polyester fabric, which has excellent rain resistance and strength. The premium TG fabric uses composite polyester cotton fabric for superior breathability, helping to prevent condensation from forming inside your awning, while also providing excellent water resistance. Both include zippable mesh panels, however, to improve ventilation, as well as a canopy over the entrance to keep you try when entering or leaving.

  • Double interior sleeping tents with darkened fabric
  • SabreLink compatible

  • Four inflation points
  • Zippable mesh panels
  • Canopy over entrance

Go camping in any vehicle

  • Zippable mesh panels behind doorways

  • Fully inflatable with two inflation points

Product Name: Bullfinch Shower Outlet Point for Campervans and Motorhomes
Product Description:
Bullfinch Shower Outlet Point for Campervans and Motorhomes

The Bullfinch External Shower Outlet is supplied with a plug in shower hose which is ideal for Campervans and Motorhomes.

Overview

The Bullfinch External Shower Outlet is available in white or grey is a complete shower assembly unit which includes the shower fitting, hose and swivelling head. Using your current water system you can easy attached the shower assembly and control the water temperature. Featuring a no-connection no-flow system this adds security to the system prevent water from spilling out if the shower assembly is not secured correctly.

Installation

To fit the Bullfinch external shower assembly you will need to core a hole with the diameter of 60mm in order to mount the utility box on the side or rear of your van, we then supply 4 fixing screws once you have done this you just need to link the shower point up to your current water system and attach the shower head assembly.

Features:

  • Complete Shower Assembly with fixing screws
  • Lightweight
  • Push & turn activation
  • High flow rate
  • John Guest Speed fit compatible. Please note these are 15mm fittings so 2 reducers will be required if using a 12mm John Guest system. Please see the related products below.

Safety & Aftercare

Please ensure when the unit is not in use in winter that you drain down the shower system, failure to do this can damage due to water inside the unit freezing - you can also prevent this by putting isolation feeds before the shower unit.

Product Name: Truma Gas Filter with Filter Pad
Product Description:
Truma Gas filter with Filter Pad

The easy way to extend your gas system's lifespan

The Truma Gasfilter effectively protects your gas system from contamination, potentially extending its lifespan dramatically. By filtering up to 99.9% of the aerosols in your gas supply, this propane, butane and LPG filter ensures your gas pressure regulators, pipes and connectors have a long service life. This makes the Truma Gas filter a great investment - it can reduce the amount of maintenance required in our gas system significantly in the long term. The filter pad absorbs the oily particles which can be produced by gas systems in campervans, caravans and motorhomes, ensuring your gas system remains clean and pure.

Tool-free operation

The pads on this filter can be changed without the need for tools, making it easy to check the condition of your filter pad on the go. What's more, safe operation is ensured by the filter's safety catch, which only allows the filter to be opened when your gas cylinder has been turned off. The filter is suitable for all wall and ceiling-mounted Truma gas regulators with M20 x 1.5 screw inlet connections.

Product Description:
Thetford T2138 12V Compressor Fridge Freezer for Campers & Motorhomes

Large Leisure Refrigeration

The Thetford T2138 12v refrigerator is perfect for large campervans, motorhomes, caravans and boats. This impressive compressor fridge stands at a mighty 1.6m tall, making it perfect for adding convenience to standing-height vehicles. The fridge is based on the design of Thetford's popular T2090, which they have extended in order to provide even more storage. This extra space makes it a great choice or extended touring - 138 litres of food storage space ensure you don't have to compromise on your cooking on the road, or change your travel plans to incorporate a supermarket.

Smart CI-BUS Control

The Thetford T2138 camper fridge features a capacitive touch panel, making it easy to select your desired operation mode at the flick of a finger. This compressor fridge also features both a night operation mode, which has both reduced energy usage and ultra low noise, letting you get a good nights sleep, and ensuring you have battery power for breakfast. Thetford have also integrated Smart CI-BUS technology into this fridge, which ensures it can communicate with the latest campervan, caravan and motorhome smart control panels for seamless operation. What's more, the fridge's intelligent management systems provide it with automatic temperature control, letting you focus on your journey.

Elegant by design

Thetford have finished this fridge in a modern matte black, allowing it to match the interior of any camper, caravan or motorhome. The flush door handle contributes to this minimal, understated design, while also maintaining the flat front profile of the fridge. The rear of the fridge tapers towards the top, allowing it to match the curvature of roofs in campervans, caravans and marine environments. The interior of the fridge features clear slide-out storage boxes, shelf food retainers and a bottle & vegetable drawer.

The Bullfinch Outdoor Water Inlet Point is equipped with a pressure limiter which is set to 1.5 bar, this is to prevent damage to the internal pipe work and any additional equipment installed. The connections that are required are John Guest speed fit (12mm) this makes installation easier.

Features:

Product Name: Thetford Duo Tank Cleaner Concentrated for Waste Tank & Grey Water Tank
Product Description:
Thetford Duo Tank Cleaner Concentrated for Waste Tank & Grey Water Tank

Powerful periodic cleaner for removing limescale and grease from waste water tanks

Thetford's Duo Tank Cleaner Chemical is ideal for when your waste tanks need a deep clean. This heavy-duty cleaner will extend the lifespan of your tanks, removing, dirt, grime and limescale to prevent wear and deterioration to your waste tank. Thetford's special formula ensures this cleaning can take part without any effort on your part - no scrubbing is required!

Fresh scent 

Thetford have imbued this orange cleaner with an attractive citrus fragrance, ensuring your grey water tank and waste tank will smell even better than they did when new. This concentrated cleaner is designed not to damage your cassette toilet's waste tank, shower's grey waste water tank, or sink grey water tank This makes it perfect for cleaning and renewing water systems on campervans, motorhomes and caravans. 

Usage

Before use

Thetford recommend that you empty each tank at least 16 hours before application. If possible, rinse thoroughly with clean water. Thetford recommends that you use this toilet chemical 2-3 times a year for the best results.

Cassette Waste Holding Tank

  1. Add 200ml to the empty tank
  2. Add 5L of lukewarm water
  3. Shake the tank vigorously several times to ensure all corners are cleaned. Driving with the cassette will also improve cleaning performance. Carefully vent the internal pressure before opening the blade.

Grey Water Tank

  1. Add 600ml to the empty tank via the sink of showerdrain
  2. Add 50L of lukewarm water
  3. Drive with your camper, motorhome or caravan for at least an hour in order to cover all sides of the tank.

Product Name: Shower and Bathroom Kit - Toilet, Shower, Sink and Tray Kit for Campervan Conversions
Product Description:
Shower and Bathroom Kit - Toilet, Shower, Sink and Tray Kit for Campervan Conversions

Fully compatible, high quality and great value

Our shower and bathroom kit combines some of the most popular and successful bathroom products for campervans together in one kit. With the components included in this kit, you can be sure you're receiving parts which are trusted and recommended by ourselves. 

What's included?

In this kit you will receive ten of our most popular bathroom products:

  • Thetford C220 Cassette Toilet
  • Thetford cassette rear access door (door 3)
  • Cleo tip-up basin
  • Cleo cabinet with mirror
  • Shower tray with cut-out for toilet
  • Shower with installation bar
  • Mixer tap for basin
  • Mixer tap for shower
  • Waste outlet drain for shower tray
  • Waste outlet drain for basin
  • Water fill door (only with C224CW)

Ideal for campervan conversions and motorhomes

We offer a choice between the C223CS - with a 12v electric flush - and the C224CW, which uses a quiet yet powerful piston pump system. The included rear access door lets you slide the cassette out of the side of your van elegantly, making it easy to dispose of your toilet's waste water. The Cleo tip-up basin and mirror cabinet are lightweight and compact, designed around the needs of the camper bathroom. Equally, the shower tray is custom designed to fit around a C223CS or C224CW, giving a flush, water-tight finish. 

The included mixer tap fits with the Cleo sink, and the shower mixer tap provides elegant control over the shower system. A bar mount system lets you adjust your shower height, just as you would at home, and the lightweight Cleo cabinet gives you a mirror with storage. The waste outlets are the correct size for the shower tray and sink, allowing you to route waste water into your waste tank elegantly.

How much space do I need to fit a bathroom?

Everything in this kit can be fitted within the width of the shower tray.

  • L/H Tray measures 1157mm x 697mm (+/- 5mm)
  • R/H tray measures 1070mm x 700mm (+/- 5mm)
  • However, both can be trimmed down to a minimum of  940mm x 675mm if required

PLEASE NOTE: The shower tray side option refers to which side the shower tray is on as you are sat on the toilet.

Thule Foothill 2 Soft Shell Tent

The Thule Tepui Foothill rooftop tent is the ultimate for the adventurer. This compact rooftop tent from Thule covers approximately half of a vehicle's roof (car dependent), giving you ample room to fit a bike or kayak.

The Thule Tepui Foothill rooftop tent uses a low-profile, symmetrical design, which allows the tent to be mounted on either side of your car for easy access in any location, and easy removal when not in use. Travel without limits

The Thule Autana 3 man rooftop tent lets you travel anywhere your car can take you. With a Thule rooftop tent, you no longer have to worry about finding a stable, dry and safe spot to pitch your tent - there's been one on top of your car, 4x4 or campervan all along. 

All-weather comfort

The Thule Autana rooftop tent comes equipped with coated 600 denier fabric with a 260g poly-cotton blend, which enables it to withstand the worst of any season. What's more, this fabric is both UV and mould resistant -  it's built to last. Mesh panels improve airflow, which helps to reduce condensation and humidity, and four large internal pockets let you store camping accessories and night essentials.

Be ready for any environment

Whether you need a reliable pitch in the desert, in the marshes, the urban jungle, or need extra space for the kids in your campervan, Thule's Tepui Autana roof tents give you a reliable, fuss-free way to do it.  Included with this roof tent is a extended private canopy entrance with a removable annex, a folding entrance ladder and a high-density foam mattress, all designed to fit perfectly.

  • UV and mould resistant fabric with 600 denier 260g poly-cotton

Product Description:

Perfect for extending your battery life

Sargent's handy solar panel kit gives you everything you need to install a high efficiency solar panel to your campervan, caravan or motorhome. Alongside the 100 watt monocrystalline solar panel, this kit includes a premium 15A Sargent MPPT charge controller to maximise the output from your solar panel, alloy L fitting feet and screws to fit.

A polyurethane adhesive sealant such as sikaflex, in combination with the included fittings, will give you an ideal installation.

Product Name: CBE BTMG LPG Soporific Gas Detector
Product Description:
CBE BTMG LPG Soporific Gas Detector

Keep you and your family safe

This CBE gas detector sounds an alarm when soporific - sleep-inducing - gas is detected in your campervan, caravan, motorhome or boat. This brings peace of mind, letting you get a good nights sleep alongside your gas installations - but not too good a sleep!

Essential safety device for campervans

This gas detector is capable of detecting common camping gases such as butane, propane, and their mixtures before they reach dangerous levels. The device has two calibration levels, allowing you to adjust the sensitivity depending on the device's location. A visual (LED) and acoustic (buzzer alarm) trigger alert you to high levels of these gases, keeping you safe from drowsiness, explosions and ill health. The device is supplied with 50cm long power cables and an installation manual, including positioning guidance.

Inflatable SUP paddle board kit complete with pump, paddle and rucksack

The Sandbanks Hawaii board can handle it all. For tackling the waves, this iSUP features a rocker (an upturn) at the nose, ensuring handling remains predictable and stable. And for gliding though smooth lakes, the hydrodynamic shaping increases the efficiency of your board, giving you greater distance with every paddle. 

Safe and easy to use

The details on this SUP ensure it's easy for beginners to use, and for experts to exploit. Quick to inflate and lightweight

Product Name: Thule Slide-Out 12v Automatic Step for Fiat Ducato Campervans
Product Description:
Thule Slide-Out 12v Automatic Step for Ducato/Boxer/Relay

With custom bracket set to fit

Available in 3 different sizes, this step allows you an easy entrance and exit from your campervan by mounting under the sliding door of your vehicle. This strong yet lightweight design is perfect for aiding mobility or simply for a confident step into your campervan, making it ideal for leisure use.

Robust design

Thule have equipped this step with rubber grip-strips, ensuring they provide excellent traction even in wet conditions. It also uses a single cable entry point, minimising the possibility of water or dust ingress. Integrated brushes help to prevent grime from entering the step from the front, too. A corrugated aluminium construction provides lightweight strength, and a rounded front profile means there are no sharp edges along the front side. 

Use it anywhere

Thanks to the 12v powered design, this step can slide out and retract at the push of a button. Worried about it getting stuck when your battery is empty? The Thule slide-out step can be stowed without the use of tools in the case of power failure, ensuring it won't jeopardize your trip. Included as standard is a switch which can be wired to a warning light in your vehicle, providing a visual signal to stop you from driving away with the step extended. Available as an optional extra is the 12v relay, which, when wired to your vehicle correctly, can retract the step automatically when your vehicle's engine starts.

Compatibility - fitting kit included

This G2 Thule step is compatible with Fiat Ducato, Peugeot Boxer and Citroën Jumper vans, campervans and motorhomes from 2007 onwards with the Euro 6 engine. We supply this step with the required mounting kit included. The depth of this kit is designed to fit vehicles with the Euro 6d-Temp engine.

The Thule Slide-out step is the perfect addition to your caravan, campervan and motorhome offering a convenient and practical way to enter your vehicle. This step can be fitted to both caravan and motorhomes, however, there are multiple variations available, and some that are vehicle specific and will require the selection of particular models or additional parts. If you are unsure, please contact us for support.

Thule Ducato Omnistep slide out step features:

  • Contemporary design
  • Rubber non-slip strips
  • Integrated brushes to reduce dust ingress
  • No sharp edges along front profile
  • Robust corrugated anodized aluminium construction
  • Switch for a warning light to prevent driveaway with the step extended included as standard

Product Name: Thule Omnistep Slide-Out 12v Automatic Step for VW Crafter Campervans
Product Description:
Thule Omnistep Slide-Out 12v Automatic Step for Campervans and Motorhomes

With custom bracket set to fit VW Crafter vans

This motorized step is great for comfort and mobility, giving you a foothold when you need it and stowing neatly under your vehicle. The stable, sturdy and grippy design of this Omnistep gives you a confident step into your vehicle.

Sturdy design

Thule have used rubber grip-strips on the step, ensuring it provides excellent traction even in wet conditions. It also uses a single cable entry point, minimising the possibility of water or dust ingress. Integrated brushes help to prevent grime from entering the step from the front, too. A corrugated aluminium construction provides lightweight strength, and a rounded front profile means there are no sharp edges along the front side. 

Fully motorized

Thanks to the 12v powered design, this step can slide out and retract at the push of a button. Worried about it getting stuck when your battery is empty? The Omnistep can be stowed without the use of tools in the case of power failure, ensuring it won't jeopardize your trip. Included as standard is a switch which can be wired to a warning light in your vehicle, providing a visual signal to stop you from driving away with the step extended. Available as an optional extra is the 12v relay, which, when wired to your vehicle correctly, can retract the step automatically when your vehicle's engine starts.

Compatibility - fitting kit included

This Omnistep is compatible with Right Hand Drive VW Crafter Vans, campervans and motorhomes from 2017, the required mounting kit is included. The Thule step is not suitable UK spec for vehicles 2017 onwards due to fuel tank locations.

The Thule Omnistep is the perfect addition to your caravan, campervan and motorhome offering a convenient and practical way to enter your vehicle. The Thule Omnistep can be fitted to both caravan and motorhomes, however, there are multiple variations available, and some that are vehicle specific and will require the selection of particular models or additional parts. If you are unsure, please contact us for support.

Thule Crafter Omnistep slide out step features:

  • Contemporary design
  • Rubber non-slip strips
  • Integrated brushes to reduce dust ingress
  • No sharp edges along front profile
  • Robust corrugated anodized aluminium construction
  • Switch for a warning light to prevent driveaway with the step extended included as standard

Scanstrut Cable Seal for PV Logic Solar Panels
Product Description:
Scanstrut Horizontal Cable Seal for Campervan, Motorhome & Boat Solar Panels

Watertight Rooftop Solar Panel Sealing Solution

Available in a range of models to suit your cable needs and solar needs, including the Single Cable Seal, Double Cable Seal, and Multi Cable Seal.

The IP68 cable seals are a durable, watertight cable solution ideal for van conversions and solar installations. The Scanstrut cable seals offer long lasting protection from sun, wind and rain, and ensures a watertight, professional finish every time. Designed for durability, this horizontal cable seal has been engineered specifically for motorhome & campervans, perfect for van owners in need of a reliable solution. Built from premium marine-grade materials, designed for durable, long-lasting performance and protection from sun, wind and rain.

Perfect for rooftop applications including solar panels, light bars, and other rooftop electrical appliances. With easy-fit captive nuts for a quick and easy installation, the Scanstrut cable seal ensures a secure, waterproof finish. Perfect for any solar panels including Victron, PV Logic, and more! Super easy installation onto single cable, double cable or multiple cable solar panels and ready to assemble from the get go. The single cable seal fits cable sizes from 6-10mm (0.24"-0.39"), the double cable seal fits cable sizes from 5-6mm (0.19-0.24") and the multi cable seal fits cable sizes up to 15mm (0.59"), making them perfect for van conversions with rooftop solar panels.

Comes with pre-drilled and blank inner seals included in the box to allow for custom diameter configurations to suit your specific installation needs. Built with impact resistant UV-stable and hard-wearing materials to ensure performance and durability even in the harshest weather conditions.

Solar Panel Cable Gland Key Features:

  • 100% watertight protection
  • Compatible with a wide range of cables
  • Suitable for solar panels, light bars, rooftop lights, and other rooftop electronics
  • Professional grade sealing
  • Easy, quick, no hassle installation
  • No messy sealant on bungs
  • Constructed from premium, marine-grade materials
  • Available as single, double and multi cable seals
  • Compatible with any solar panel!
  • Suitable for motorhome, campervan, & canal boat fixed solar panels
